'''傑克·亞歷山大·休斯頓'''（{{lang-en|'''Jack Alexander Huston'''}}<ref name=peerage>[http://www.thepeerage.com The Peerage] {{Wayback|url=http://www.thepeerage.com/ |date=20201117041446 }}February 2013</ref>，{{bd|1982年|12月7日}}）是一位英國男演員。休斯頓較著名的是在[[HBO|HBO]]製作的電視劇《[[海濱帝國|海濱帝國]]》（2010年至2013年）中飾演[[理查·哈洛|理查·哈洛]]<ref>{{cite news | last=Alexander | first=Caroline | title=Faces of War  Amid the horrors of World War I, a corps of artists brought hope to soldiers disfigured in the trenches | work=Smithsonian Magazine | date=February 2007 | url=http://www.smithsonianmag.com/history/faces-of-war-145799854/#ZqbhIOceMshbS1Ak.99 | accessdate=March 15, 2014 | archive-date=2014-03-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316080508/http://www.smithsonianmag.com/history/faces-of-war-145799854/#ZqbhIOceMshbS1Ak.99 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.thedailybeast.com/jack-huston-on-boardwalk-empire-playing-richard-harrow-the-mask-and-more |title = Jack Huston on ‘Boardwalk Empire,’ Playing Richard Harrow, the Mask, and More |author = Jace Lacob |date = 2011-10-23 |publisher = Daily Beast |language = en |accessdate = 2018-08-26 |archive-date = 2020-12-16 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201216194105/https://www.thedailybeast.com/jack-huston-on-boardwalk-empire-playing-richard-harrow-the-mask-and-more |dead-url = no }}</ref>。他也於2013年電影《[[瞞天大佈局|瞞天大佈局]]》中參與配角的演出，以及在2016年歷史電影《[[賓漢_(2016年電影)|賓漢]]》中飾演{{link-en|猶大·賓漢|Judah Ben-Hur}}。

==早期生活==
休斯頓出生於[[諾福克郡|諾福克郡]][[金斯林|金斯林]]，是Lady Margot Lavinia和{{link-en|東尼·休斯頓|Tony Huston|華特·安東尼·「東尼」·休斯頓}}的兒子<ref name=peerage/>。休斯頓立志成為一名演員，在六歲的時候，他曾在學校的話劇《[[彼得潘|彼得潘]]》上擔任主角<ref>[http://www.zimbio.com/Jack+Huston/articles/NZwXZaPhgrR/Spotlight+new+Eclipse+actor+Jack+Huston] {{Webarchive|url=https://archive.today/20130412053645/http://www.zimbio.com/Jack+Huston/articles/NZwXZaPhgrR/Spotlight+new+Eclipse+actor+Jack+Huston |date=2013-04-12 }} zimbio.com-Jack Huston</ref>。後來，他就讀了著名的戲劇學校{{link-en|赫特伍德學院|Hurtwood House}}<ref>[http://www.hurtwoodhouseperformingarts.co.uk/#/jack-huston/4536855573] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hurtwoodhouseperformingarts.co.uk/#/jack-huston/4536855573 |date=20100221214533 }} hurtwood house performing arts-jack-huston</ref>。

